snippet.title: Best VGM 2270 - Grandia II - Carbo Village ~ Pious Adepts
snippet.description:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Dreamcast / Playstation 2 / PC
Grandia II (2000)
Carbo Village ~ Pious Adepts
Noriyuki Iwadare
